Debian Live USB for network testing

Debian 7

Development tools
	apt-get install vim subversion git-core
X Windows

	aptitude install --without-recommends xorg
	aptitude install --without-recommends lxde
Languages
?	aptitude install --without-recommends uim uim-anthy
Sound
?	aptitude install alsa-utils

Windows applications

?	aptitude install --without-recommends midori
Network tools
	apt-get install iperf
